            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x0,
            "msg_string": "Looks like you've gotten pretty strong, Sophie."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2a,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Huh? You can tell?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x9,
            "name_id": 0x9,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "I can tell somewhat from the condition of your weapons, and your appearance."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x17,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0x3,
            "msg_string": "I see. Ehehe, I'm happy about that."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x9,
            "name_id": 0x9,
            "extra_id": 0x5,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x4,
            "msg_string": "Yeah... It should be fine telling you about this now."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x19,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0x5,
            "msg_string": "About what?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x9,
            "name_id": 0x9,
            "extra_id": 0x2b,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x6,
            "msg_string": "If you go north from this town, you'll find an \"Underground Lake\". You can collect great ores and minerals there."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x9,
            "name_id": 0x9,
            "extra_id": 0x2d,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x7,
            "msg_string": "You might be able to use them as materials for alchemy, too."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x30,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x8,
            "msg_string": "Huh, there's a place like that? But... Why are you telling me now?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x9,
            "name_id": 0x9,
            "extra_id": 0x69,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x9,
            "msg_string": "There are pretty dangerous monsters there. You need to be pretty strong to go there, or you'd be in real danger."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x9,
            "name_id": 0x9,
            "extra_id": 0x6b,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xa,
            "msg_string": "I think you would be fine going there now, though."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x32,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xb,
            "msg_string": "I see."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x9,
            "name_id": 0x9,
            "extra_id": 0x43,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xc,
            "msg_string": "I just have a feeling you'd be okay. You could even go there to test your strength."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x40,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xd,
            "msg_string": "Okay, thank you very much."
        },
